BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:pfX14irh6Ue_33s3z0GQY
SUMMARY:Multivers - Multiplayer 1v1v1v1 x Multivers
DTSTAMP:20260320T051445Z
DTSTART:20260320T183000Z
DTEND:20260320T213000Z
DESCRIPTION:Ce vendredi au Multivers\, ce sera construit Mulijoueureuses !\
	n\nFormat : Construit Multiplayer Free-for-all 1v1v1v1\nStructure : 3 (ou 
	4 selon le temps) rondes suisses (pour déterminer les tables suivantes par
	 résultat)\nTemps des rondes : 1 heure\nHoraires : 19h30-23h\n\nPrécision 
	de règle : \n- Only 3 battlefield. First turn player doesn't get to use on
	e of their own battlefields\, the remaining three players get to choose a 
	battlefield each.\n- First player doesn't get to draw a card on their firs
	t turn. Second and third get to draw a card and have the standard 2 runes.
	 Final player gets to draw and channel the third rune.\n- Rule 632.1.b.2 :
	\nIf the player has Scored through a Conquer and has Scored every Battlefi
	eld through either method this turn\, that player scores the Final Point. 
	If the player has Scored through a Conquer and has not Scored every Battle
	field this turn\, that player draws a card.\n\nProxy : autorisation maximu
	m de 10% du total du deck (soit jusqu'à 5 cartes avec le side)\nMERCI de v
	enir avec des proxy print de qualité acceptable et de le préciser à vos ad
	versaires avant le match. \n\nDotations : \n1 booster Riftbound Origins pa
	r participant.e\nTop 3 : 1 booster Origins supplémentaire\nGagnant.e : 1 b
	ooster Origins supplémentaire\n\nAmbiance à la cool 💖
URL:https://locator.riftbound.uvsgames.com/events/454992
GEO:48.8433885;2.3813034
LOCATION:81 Rue du Charolais\, Ground Control\, Paris\, IDF\, 75012\, FR
LAST-MODIFIED:20260320T051400Z
END:VEVENT
